CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782703089
OL,3,CBrooch given to first passenger to
OL,4,Cboard doomed steamship found at
OL,5,Croadshow
OL,7,FThe shipping firm was owned by William
OL,8,FRobertson, who started out with a
OL,9,Fsingle barge in 1852 before growing it
OL,10,Finto one of the largest coastal bulk
OL,11,Fshipping fleets in Britain.
OL,13,FThe brooch was presented to Ms
OL,14,FAnderson by Mr Robertson and is
OL,15,Finscribed with the words "SS Citrine,
OL,16,FApril 21 1894, Elizabeth McIntyre
OL,17,FAnderson, from William Robertson".
OL,26,@wD@ZOUyD@aO]
