OL,3,CBrooch given to first passenger to
OL,4,Cboard doomed steamship found at
OL,5,Croadshow
OL,7,FWilliam Robertson had been dead for 12
OL,8,Fyears by the time of the sinking but
OL,9,Fthe business remained in family hands
OL,10,Funder his sons, William Francis
OL,11,FRobertson and James Robertson.
OL,13,FThe brooch was discovered at a
OL,14,FWeBuyVintage roadshow in Fleetwood,
OL,15,FLancashire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
