OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782703089
OL,3,CBrooch given to first passenger to
OL,4,Cboard doomed steamship found at
OL,5,Croadshow
OL,7,FThe antiques firm said the man who
OL,8,Fbrought it in explained it had passed
OL,9,Fdown through his late wife's family
OL,10,Fthrough one of her uncles ` meaning it
OL,11,Fhas remained in the family since it
OL,12,Fwas given to Ms Anderson more than 130
OL,13,Fyears ago.
OL,15,FThe brooch is expected to sell for
OL,16,F#100 but WeBuyVintage specialist Matt
OL,17,FCase said its true value lies
OL,18,Felsewhere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
