OL,3,CBrooch given to first passenger to
OL,4,Cboard doomed steamship found at
OL,5,Croadshow
OL,7,F"While the value of the brooch is low
OL,8,Fin monetary terms, it is far more than
OL,9,Fjust a piece of decorative jewellery,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,F"It is a rare and poignant survivor of
OL,13,FScotland's maritime history.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@fO]tD@AOU
