OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782703089
OL,3,CBrooch given to first passenger to
OL,4,Cboard doomed steamship found at
OL,5,Croadshow
OL,7,F"Connected to a specific ship, a named
OL,8,Frecipient, a launch date and
OL,9,Fultimately a vessel lost in an
OL,10,Finfamous wreck, it provides an
OL,11,Fextraordinary link between Dundee
OL,12,Fcraftsmanship, Glasgow's commercial
OL,13,Fambition and the human story behind
OL,14,Fone of the nation's lost steamers."
